Earlier on at the same venue, Cheruiyot-led Bunge FC lost 4-3 to the Kericho County Assembly FC in an entertaining encounter. Tea Research Institute FC beat Galaxy FC 2-0 to win Senator Kiptoiyot Tournament in a fiercely contested final at Kericho Green Stadium on Saturday.
The tournament, sponsored by Kericho Senator Aaron Cheruiyot, saw the winners bag Sh500,000 and a trophy in a competition attended by several legislators both from the Senate and the National Assembly.



